            , having stollen 3 Wiggs, went into the Prosecutor's House to see if they were good, where spying a Door in a private Place, they unbolted it, and coming in the Night, found the Family had not bolted it again, so the Prisoner and Barker went in and stole the Goods, while he stood Gammon (i.e. to watch that no body came to surprize them.) But there being no Evidence but Gardiner's against the Prisoner, the Jury <rs id="t17170717-10-verdict51" type="verdictDescription">
